// Unlike the other testbeds, `testbed_full_ui` is a single static screen with no scene
// states, so it cannot use `helpers::switch_scene_in_ci`. A one-shot `ScreenshotAndExit`
// at a fixed frame (stable filename: `screenshot-100.png`) gives it golden-image coverage
// on Pixel Eagle consistent with the other testbeds.
(
    setup: (
        fixed_frame_time: Some(0.05),
    ),
    events: [
        (100, ScreenshotAndExit),
    ]
)
